Syntax:
digit := [0123456789]
[+]?{digit}+>[Uu]?[Dd]?[Ll]?[Rr]?[Ss]?[Pp]|-?{digit}+ -?{digit}+|-?{digit}+ -?{digit}+ -?{digit}+ -?{digit}+ -?{digit}+

Command:
[Tick to Activate]>{Player Inputs}|<Relative Mouse X> <Relative Mouse Y>
+[Tick after Previous]>{Player Inputs}|<Relative Mouse X> <Relative Mouse Y>

Player Inputs:
U - Hold up
u - Release up
D - Hold down
d - Release down
L - Hold left
l - Release left
R - Hold right
r - Release right
S - Toggle on sprint
S - Toggle off sprint
P - Enter focus mode (left click)
p - Leave focus mode (right click)